  <brief_title>Evaluation the Safety and Efficacy of Cilostazol in Treatment of Patients With Fatty Liver Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation the Safety and Efficacy of Cilostazol in Treatment of Patients With Fatty Liver Disease: A Randomized, Controlled Trial.</official_title>
