  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the current study is to evaluate the safety and efficay of cilostazol in treatment&#xD;
      of patients with fatty liver disease. Several previous reports have shown that cilostazol&#xD;
      ameliorates lipid imbalances in NAFLD. Cilostazol appeared to exert beneficial effects&#xD;
      against NAFLD&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
